query:
SELECT g.numero FROM gafetes g
                 LEFT JOIN ingresos_visitas iv ON g.numero = iv.gafete AND iv.estado = 'ADENTRO'
                 WHERE g.tipo = 'visita' AND g.estado = 'activo'
                 AND iv.id IS NULL AND g.numero != 'S/G' AND g.is_deleted = 0
                 ORDER BY g.numero
